select date_trunc('minute', fechahora) - (CAST(extract(minute from fechahora) as integer) % 5) * interval '1 minute' as fechahora, dispositivo, atributo, avg(valor) as valor FROM openiot.th_sensores group by date_trunc('minute', fechahora) - (CAST(extract(minute from fechahora) as integer) % 5) * interval '1 minute', dispositivo, atributo order by date_trunc('minute', fechahora) - (CAST(extract(minute from fechahora) as integer) % 5) * interval '1 minute', dispositivo, atributo;
